data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 2-car garage  at Bay Colony West community.  Inside, you'll find an open layout with a spacious kitchen featuring espresso cabinets, granite countertops, and lots of natural light. The living room is bright and welcoming.  This home is conveniently located near schools, a pool, and a park, offering plenty of recreational options. Access to HWY 45 makes commuting easy, and the home is flood-free, even during Hurricane Harvey. This is a comfortable, convenient, and charming opportunity. Schedule a showing today!
